para_trans: With the expiry of the term of the Great Nation Men's Biographical Instruments Publication Committees, regarding the extension of these Committees.
Department of Higher and Technical Education
Government Decision No: Sankauran 2024 / Q. 49/946792 MASHI-2
Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,

Reference: - 1. Government Decision, Department of Higher and Technical Education No. Sankarna-2024 / Q. 22/721067 Masi-2, D. 1.7.2024 2. Government Decision Department of Higher and Technical Education No. Sankarna-2021 / P.S. No.198 / Aastha-D. 25.10.2021

Government Decision: - Reference No. Under Government Decisions 1 and 2, the period of publication committees for the following brochures under the Department of Higher and Technical Education was extended. With the expiry of this extension, all these Committees are being extended till 15th May, 2025 or till the reconstitution of the Committees, whichever is earlier.
The Government decision was made available on the Government of Maharashtra website 4www.maharashtra.gov.in.
